The package boost-lexical-cast is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS lexical_cast)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::lexical_cast)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_lexical_cast REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::lexical_cast)
